query:
-- Consolidate Nevada, Placer, Sierra, Sutter, Yuba to Sierra-Sacramento Valley
UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'Sierra-Sacramento Valley EMS Agency' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND (LOWER(name) LIKE '%nevada%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%placer%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%sierra%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%sutter%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%yuba%') AND name != 'Sierra-Sacramento Valley EMS Agency' AND LOWER(name) NOT LIKE '%sierra-sacramento%');

-- Consolidate Solano
UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'Solano County EMS' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND LOWER(name) LIKE '%solano%' AND name != 'Solano County EMS');

-- Consolidate Stanislaus
UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'Stanislaus County EMS Agency' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND LOWER(name) LIKE '%stanislaus%' AND name != 'Stanislaus County EMS Agency');

-- Consolidate Ventura
UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'Ventura County EMS Agency' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND LOWER(name) LIKE '%ventura%' AND name != 'Ventura County EMS Agency');

-- Consolidate Yolo
UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'Yolo County EMS Agency' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND LOWER(name) LIKE '%yolo%' AND name != 'Yolo County EMS Agency');
